&lt;Novamin Inc> saidits board will recommend to shareholders the takeover offermade by Breakwater Resources Ltd.    Breakwater is offering to exchange one Breakwater share foreach two shares of Novamin, the company said.    Breakwater will issue about 3.7 mln shares for all Novaminshares presently issued and outstanding. Additional shraes ofBreakwater will be issued if warrants and options of Novaminare exercised. Reuter&#3;